    <p>Old Girls’ Association (OGA) of Fathima Muslim Ladies’ College was established in year 2000 by the head prefect of that time Mrs. Menza Hussain. It was initially started with only 25 members and later and gradually expanded but as of now over 250 Lifetime memberships have been issued.</p>
